%I A396482 #9 Jun 02 2026 06:51:50
%S A396482 1,2,12,372,14844,1945432,322491011
%N A396482 Number of undirected Hamiltonian paths in the mod n square grid graph, reduced for symmetry (with rotations, reflections, and translations not counted as distinct).
%C A396482 Here a "mod n square grid graph" is a n X n graph with wrapping allowed, e.g., a path can make a 1 unit step between the left and the right edge (same row) or the top and the bottom edge (same column) of the graph.
%e A396482 a(3) = 12: 3 symmetric cases:
%e A396482                                     :
%e A396482   X--+--+       X--+--+       X--+  +
%e A396482         |             |          |  |
%e A396482 ..+--+  +..     +--+--+     ..X  +  +..
%e A396482      |          |                |
%e A396482 ..X  +--+..     +--+--X     ..+--+  +..
%e A396482                                     :
%e A396482 plus 9 nonsymmetric cases:
%e A396482                                                                 :
%e A396482   X--+--+       X--+--+       X--+--+       X--+  X       X--+  +
%e A396482         |             |             |          |  |          |  |
%e A396482   +--X  +       +--+  +       X  +--+     ..+  +  +..   ..+  +  +..
%e A396482   |     |       |  |  |       |  |          |  |          |  |
%e A396482   +--+--+       X  +--+     ..+  +--+..   ..+  +--+..     X  +--+
%e A396482                                                                 :
%e A396482   X--+--+       X--+--+       X--+--+       X--+--+
%e A396482         |             |             |             |
%e A396482 ..+--+  +..   ..+  X  +..     X--+  +       +--+  +
%e A396482      |          |  |             |  |       |  |  |
%e A396482 ..+--+  X..   ..+  +--+..   ..+--+  +..   ..+  X  +..
%Y A396482 Cf. A268838, A395462 (all undirected paths, reduced), A396483 (Hamiltonian cycles), A265914 (wrapping disallowed).
%K A396482 nonn,walk,hard,more,new
%O A396482 1,2
